mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f1280d7d706fd3545b4a431616e4cc5568aa86","tid":185571,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"竟然冇乾杯"},{"pid":"05bbb1c19ec685f4966d330e833fc3c39fb03c10","tid":185571,"uid":96858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"人生海海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1df4c73265fe8e4e1fce3291d6c6d3562f5354d","tid":185571,"uid":63776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307bb3010c2551c28b243dee0d64b574bc83b1b6","tid":185571,"uid":89137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"將軍令"},{"pid":"0f2768bb2d044a64a2d36f026b1cf274d3193cbb","tid":185571,"uid":99159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如煙<br />\nD詞屈機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 聽完真係覺得人生苦短"},{"pid":"6eb285240178e4b788f50413fc217840e1a980c6","tid":185571,"uid":14315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"近排喺第二人生"},{"pid":"8273c3b9488d9dff5ddf957b41f37cf32c356cd0","tid":185571,"uid":102655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然冇乾杯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係喎乾杯都要上榜 送首乾杯比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會不會 有一天 時間真的能倒退<br />\n退回 你的我的 回不去的 悠悠的歲月<br />\n<br />\n也許會 有一天 世界真的有終點<br />\n也要和你舉起回憶釀的甜 和你再乾一杯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果說 要我選出 代表青春 那個畫面<br />\n浮現了 那滴眼淚 那片藍天 那年畢業<br />\n那一張 邊哭邊笑 還要擁抱 是你的臉<br />\n想起來 可愛可憐 可歌可泣 可是多懷念<br />\n<br />\n懷念總是 突然懷念 不談條件<br />\n當回憶 衝破考卷 衝出歲月 在我眼前<br />\n我和你 留著汗水 喝著汽水 在操場邊<br />\n說好了 無論如何 一起走到 未來的世界<br />\n<br />\n現在就是 那個未來 那個世界<br />\n為什麼 你的身邊 我的身邊 不是同一邊<br />\n<br />\n友情曾像 諾亞方舟 堅強誓言<br />\n只是我 望著海面 等著永遠 模糊了視線<br />\n<br />\n會不會 有一天 時間真的能倒退<br />\n退回 你的我的 回不去的 悠悠的歲月<br />\n<br />\n也許會 有一天 世界真的有終點<br />\n也要和你舉起回憶釀的甜 和你再乾一杯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這些年 買了四輪 買了手錶 買了單眼<br />\n卻發現 追不到的 停不了的 還是那些<br />\n人生是 只有認命 只能宿命 只好宿醉<br />\n只剩下 高的笑點 低的哭點 卻沒成熟點<br />\n<br />\n成熟就是 幻想幻滅 一場磨練<br />\n為什麼 只有夢想 越磨越小 小到不見<br />\n有時候 好想流淚 好想流淚 卻沒眼淚<br />\n期待會 你會不會 他會不會 開個同學會<br />\n<br />\n他在等你 你在等我 我在等誰<br />\n又是誰 孩子沒睡 電話沒電 心情沒準備<br />\n<br />\n天空不斷 黑了又亮 亮了又黑<br />\n那光陰 滄海桑田 遠走高飛 再沒力氣追<br />\n<br />\n會不會 有一天 時間真的能倒退<br />\n退回 你的我的 回不去的 悠悠的歲月<br />\n也許會 有一天 世界真的有終點<br />\n也要和你舉起回憶釀的甜 和你再乾一杯<br />\n<br />\n會不會 有一天 時間真的能倒退<br />\n退回 你的我的 回不去的 悠悠的歲月<br />\n也許會 有一天 世界真的有終點<br />\n也要和你舉起回憶釀的甜 和你再乾一杯<br />\n<br />\n終究會 有一天 我們都變成昨天<br />\n是你 陪我走過 一生一回 匆匆的人間<br />\n<br />\n有一天 就是今天 今天就是有一天<br />\n說出一直沒說 對你的感謝 和你再乾一杯<br />\n再乾一杯永遠 喝了就能萬歲 歲歲和年年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間都停了 他們都回來了<br />\n懷念的人啊 等你的來到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qX2GsMj7154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqX2GsMj7154&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5InIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=effb640c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qX2GsMj7154</a>"},{"pid":"a4e81b7b01f9ff777e2ad17f336682f1aa984d76","tid":185571,"uid":2183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"傷心的人別聽慢歌<br />\n<br />\n通常好灰既時候聽"},{"pid":"b2fbd12281fb3191db91cdb67b7347bb8b33a055","tid":185571,"uid":8574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"知足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於你身影消失在人海之中<br />\n才發現 笑著哭 最痛<br />\n<br />\n星空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 自己本身好鍾意睇星 聽呢首歌好有feel)<br />\n至少回憶會永久 像不變星空 陪著我<br />\n<br />\n求同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fd70e071f4aa9eba75384e3994a21399437d2d","tid":185571,"uid":35758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"近幾年真係2012同諾亞方舟最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca38529333737e2cec26bcd28d1d0d486ef4eb6","tid":185571,"uid":65625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"就像我的生活 一直在出差錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0036a80ed555bc4fce71f75514ade1b399d63bfa","tid":185571,"uid":23137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:33:11.000Z","msg":"步步"},{"pid":"6b22a94ea2004b1a1c90296cd3259a060fcc5746","tid":185571,"uid":25958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倔強</blockquote><br />\n+1 <br />\n我和我最後的倔強 握緊雙手絕對不放<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申好想現場大合唱一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454612a29aa358cd7efc5971bf24b60079ad49c","tid":185571,"uid":25958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"近期愛上了忘詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fabe175d216d07a1e27e0f40b37e9b68dc4456","tid":185571,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"倔強啦"},{"pid":"acde2ff3f9e9748367f1d5ef993e10f142d829e6","tid":185571,"uid":99159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"Do u ever shine? 國語版都唔錯<br />\n但只有演唱會限定"},{"pid":"72d632f47d5ad42bf525561532a1e59bcd8975dd","tid":185571,"uid":92412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"一定係乾杯<br />\n歌詞正不特至 睇親個mv實喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"